# Welcome to Soutik Chakraborty's Project Page
Hello this is Soutik Chakraborty - Master's Student at University of Washington, Seattle studying Information Management specialisation in Data Science & Analytics. You will find all my data science projects here!

Please feel free to contact me at soutikc@uw.edu for any opportunities or collaborations

## Projects
***
***
### NYC School SAT score analysis
***
 
In this project I took the NYC city school data and did some analysis showcasing trends in SAT scores from each school and then figuring out which are the best schools for high SAT score outcome.

Find the code and output here : [NYC SAT score analysis](http://soutik.github.io/NYC-school-SAT-score)

To download/fork the code click here : [Github code - NYC SAT score analysis](https://github.com/soutik/NYC-school-SAT-score)
